---
export const prerender = true;
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<BlogLayout
  title="Scrabble Words from Skiing — Snow Sport Terms That Score Big"
  description="Skiing and snow sport words valid in Scrabble with full scoring. SLALOM (8pts), MOGUL (8pts), PISTE (7pts). Winter sport vocabulary for competitive Scrabble players."
  keywords="scrabble skiing words, slalom scrabble points, mogul scrabble, piste scrabble, snow sport words scrabble, winter vocabulary scrabble, ski terms scrabble"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Article","headline":"Scrabble Words from Skiing — Snow Sport Terms That Score Big","description":"Skiing and snow sport words valid in Scrabble with full scoring. SLALOM (8pts), MOGUL (8pts), PISTE (7pts).","datePublished":"2026-06-30","author":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com","url":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"ScrabbleWordsFinder.com"},"mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.scrabblewordsfinder.com/blog/scrabble-words-from-skiing"}})} />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is SLALOM a valid Scrabble word?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! SLALOM scores 8 points (S=1, L=1, A=1, L=1, O=1, M=3). The M=3 tile provides value in this well-known 6-letter skiing term. Valid in both TWL and SOWPODS dictionaries."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many points is MOGUL worth in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"MOGUL scores 8 points (M=3, O=1, G=2, U=1, L=1). A compact 5-letter word where M=3 and G=2 combine for a solid score. Also means a powerful person — dual meanings help you remember it."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you play PISTE in Scrabble?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. PISTE scores 7 points (P=3, I=1, S=1, T=1, E=1). This French-origin ski run term is valid in SOWPODS and hooks with S for PISTES (8pts). A useful P-word in tight positions."}}]})} />
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose flex items-center gap-1"><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Blog</a><span class="mx-1">›</span><span class="text-gray-300">Word Lists</span></nav>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Scrabble Words from Skiing — Snow Sport Terms That Score Big</h1>
      <div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400"><time datetime="2026-06-30">June 30, 2026</time><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><span>5 min read</span><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-600"></span><a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-blue-400 hover:underline"><span aria-hidden="true">🔤</span> Word Finder</a></div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-300 mb-8">Hit the slopes of Scrabble with skiing vocabulary. From the zigzag of SLALOM to the bumps of MOGUL, winter sport terms deliver consistent mid-range scores with board-friendly letter patterns.</p>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">14 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SCHUSS</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">8 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">SLALOM</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">8 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">MOGUL</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">7 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">PISTE</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Top-Scoring Skiing Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-8 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-amber-500/50 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-950/30 to-yellow-950/20 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-amber-500/70">👑 Top Scorer</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">SCHUSS — 14 Points</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-300 font-semibold mb-3">S=1, C=3, H=4, U=1, S=1, S=1 · 6 letters · C+H premium combo</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">A straight downhill ski run at maximum speed — and maximum Scrabble value. The C=3 and H=4 combination delivers 7 points from just two tiles, while triple S makes it easy to draw naturally.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">⛷️ SLALOM</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">8 pts · S=1, L=1, A=1, L=1, O=1, M=3 · Double L</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏔️ MOGUL</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">8 pts · M=3, O=1, G=2, U=1, L=1 · M+G combo</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🎿 PISTE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">7 pts · P=3, I=1, S=1, T=1, E=1 · P carries</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10"><p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">❄️ SCHUSS</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">14 pts · S=1, C=3, H=4, U=1, S=1, S=1 · C+H power</p></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">More Skiing Vocabulary</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">POWDER</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">12pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">CHALET</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">11pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">ALPINE</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">8pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">TRAVERSE</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">11pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">SNOWPLOW</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">16pts</span></span>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-gray-800 border border-green-500/40 text-sm"><span class="text-white font-bold">CARVE</span><span class="text-green-400 text-xs">10pts</span></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Strategy for Skiing Words</h2>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">SLALOM uses double L efficiently:</span> Drawing two L tiles often clogs your rack. SLALOM turns this liability into 8 points across 6 letters — clear the rack and score simultaneously.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">MOGUL has dual utility:</span> Valid as both a skiing bump and a powerful person. Two meanings means two memory hooks — you'll always remember this word when M and G appear together.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">SCHUSS dominates the CH combo:</span> When C and H sit together on your rack, SCHUSS delivers 14 points with common remaining tiles (U, S, S). Triple S appears often enough to make this viable.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Key Insight</p>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">Skiing words solve <span class="text-white font-medium">duplicate tile problems</span>. SLALOM (LL), SCHUSS (SSS), and MOGUL (common tiles) all absorb duplicates that would otherwise limit your options. Think snow sports when your rack looks repetitive.</p>
      </div>
      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-sports/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Sports</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-wrestling/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Wrestling</span></a>
          <a href="/blog/scrabble-words-from-weather/" class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-gray-800 hover:border-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-900/10 transition-all group"><span class="text-blue-500 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">→</span><span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Scrabble Words from Weather</span></a>
        </div>
      </aside>
      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-cyan-900/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 flex-wrap">
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-300 font-medium">🔤 Find every valid skiing word instantly — free Scrabble solver, no sign-up</p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-sm font-semibold transition-colors shadow-sm">Open Word Finder →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="not-prose mt-8 text-center"><a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">← Back to all articles</a></div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
